  "texts": [
    "\"Deep learning\" is also a high-frequency keyword, and it indicates that the \"deep learning\" method is one important focus in Chinese sentiment analysis.",
    "Such discoveries are reasonable, and consistent with previous research (Jia 2022; Wu et al. 2022).",
    "We have extracted these prominent keywords to form the foundation for our subsequent analysis.",
    "Table 1 showcases the high-frequency keywords which essentially encapsulate the primary research focus within the realm of Chinese sentiment analysis.",
    "\"Microblog\" and \"deep learning\" secures the top positions, trailed by \"social medium,\" and \"text mining\"."
  ]
}